# Content – Documentation

## Structure

- Numbered directories: `1.getting-started/`, `2.essentials/`
- Index files: `1.index.md`
- Navigation: `.navigation.yml` in directory (title, icon)

## Collections (content.config.ts)

- `landing` – homepage
- `docs` – local documentation (`content/**`, prefix `/docs`)
- `sdk_docs` – docs from external repo (GitHub)

## Schemas

Collections can have Zod schemas, e.g. `links` with `label`, `icon`, `to`, `target`.
